            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/987.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crack the<strong> egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into a shallow bowl and beat with a fork</p><p>Add 3 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [6 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> to another plate</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>fish fingers </strong>to the<strong> flour</strong> (tap off any excess), add them to the <strong>beaten egg</strong>, then put them into the bowl of <strong>herby breadcrumbs</strong> and give them a good mix up until they're fully coated</p><p>Repeat this process with the rest of the fish – these are your <strong>herby fish fingers</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/987.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
