            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>blanched peas </strong>to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiling water </strong>(just enough to cover them) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 1 min or until they're warmed through</p><p>Once tender, drain the peas<strong> </strong>and set aside</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/987.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/987.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/987.-step-6-x700.jpg",
