          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/987.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>herby fish fingers</strong> and cook for 4-5 min on each side, or until golden and cooked through (you may have to do this in batches)</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 7,
